#: ../../hardware/controllers/native_instruments_traktor_kontrol_s4_mk3.rst:2
msgid "Native Instruments Traktor Kontrol S4 MK3"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/native_instruments_traktor_kontrol_s4_mk3.rst:4
msgid ""
"The Kontrol S4 MK3 is a 4 deck all-in-one controller with a sturdy build "
"quality and integrated sound card. Compared to the MK2 and MK1, it also have"
" motorised shiny aluminum jogwheels, screens and a set of pads which can be "
"use for various features."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/native_instruments_traktor_kontrol_s4_mk3.rst:8
msgid ""
"The S4 MK3 uses the standard :term:`HID` protocol for the Buttons, Knobs, "
"Faders and LEDs, and extends it for the motorized Jog-Wheels. The screens "
"use a USB Bulk transfer. Mixxx doesn't support rendering content for "
"external screens yet. The easiest way to tell the MK3 apart from the other "
"MK1 and 2 are these screens, displace between the \"Move\" and \"Loop\" "
"encoder."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/native_instruments_traktor_kontrol_s4_mk3.rst:12
msgid ""
"Unlike its predecessor, the Kontrol S4 Mk3 cannot run from :term:`USB` power"
" and the separate power supply must be used."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/native_instruments_traktor_kontrol_s4_mk3.rst:14
msgid ""
"`Manufacturer’s product page <https://www.native-"
"instruments.com/en/products/traktor/dj-controllers/traktor-kontrol-s4/>`__"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/native_instruments_traktor_kontrol_s4_mk3.rst:17
msgid "Added beatjump"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/native_instruments_traktor_kontrol_s4_mk3.rst:19
msgid "Added stems"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/native_instruments_traktor_kontrol_s4_mk3.rst:23
msgid "Compatibility"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/native_instruments_traktor_kontrol_s4_mk3.rst:25
msgid ""
"The Kontrol S4 MK3 is a USB class compliant audio and :term:`HID`, so it is "
"compatible with Mixxx without any proprietary drivers on GNU/Linux, MacOS "
"and Windows."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/native_instruments_traktor_kontrol_s4_mk3.rst:27
msgid ""
"With the S4 plugged in, a HID device is listed as an available controller in"
" Mixxx’s Preferences. The controller uses HID for each components on the "
"device, except the screens, so the mapping can only be loaded when you "
"select the HID device on the left side of Mixxx’s Preferences."
msgstr ""

